      "message": "[🔴 Critical Issues - Must fix before merge] Line 694: Calling bwController_.setTargetBitrate(newBR) after every applied controller decision resets lastStableBitrate_ to the newly reduced bitrate. This loses the pre-congestion recovery reference saved by applyDecrease()/onAudioCongestion(), so the controller immediately treats the reduced value as stable and recovery/probing behavior is biased incorrectly. Split the sync path from the external seeding path so applying a controller-computed bitrate updates only targetBitrate_, not lastStableBitrate_.\n```suggestion\n        bwController_.syncAppliedBitrate(newBR);\n```\nImplement syncAppliedBitrate() to clamp and assign targetBitrate_ without changing lastStableBitrate_.",
